title: Corbin Bullet Swaging CDs - reloading, handloading, ammo, weapon
description:
These are the latest CDs of books from Corbin Bullet Swaging. (Bullet Swaging is the process of making your own projectiles for handloading or reloading using a reloading press.) Corbin insists on a really annoying sound track when you launch the CD, but that's Corbin. He's a tool & die maker, not a web developer.

Burn each .ISO to a CD. (They are tiny, but each has a menu, a PDF, and a few other formats of the book along with the previously mentioned annoying sound track.)
